description:
Second Activity in the smoke test sequence.

Page 1: HAS Interactive with info/assess block and snapshot of HAS interactive in carousel

Page 2: Interactive with lab table that saves state no report URL

Page 3: Arg block and Lab table that saves state in interactive with report URL.

Page 4: Info/Assess and image interactive. Snapshot no background. Make drawing.

Page 5: Change order of question and check that they stay in correct order when published.

Page 6: Test page for auto publishing.

Page 7: HAS Water model in interactive

Page 8: CODAP interactive in info/assess block and Drawing tool with background image.
